<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>갓생 업 | 온보딩</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-white border-bottom sticky-top">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/">갓생 업</a>
        <div class="ms-auto d-flex gap-2">
            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm">로그인</a>
            <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-dark btn-sm">회원가입</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<main>
    <section class="py-5 py-lg-6 bg-white border-bottom">
        <div class="container py-lg-5">
            <div class="row align-items-center g-5">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                    <span class="badge text-bg-dark mb-3">나의 하루가 내 캐릭터의 경험치가 된다</span>
                    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">작은 행동을 매일의 성장으로 바꾸는 자기관리 RPG</h1>
                    <p class="lead text-secondary mb-4">
                        오늘의 미션을 등록하고, 인증하고, 경험치를 쌓아 레벨업하세요.
                        갓생 업은 TODO를 넘어서 캐릭터 성장과 랭킹 경쟁까지 연결하는 성장형 루틴 서비스입니다.
                    </p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-dark btn-lg">지금 시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body p-4 p-lg-5">
                            <div class="row g-3 text-center">
                                <div class="col-4">
                                    <div class="border rounded-4 p-3 h-100">
                                        <img src="/images/characters/egg.png" alt="알" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="width: 88px; height: 88px; object-fit: contain;">
                                        <div class="fw-semibold">Lv 1-5</div>
                                        <div class="text-secondary small">알</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-4">
                                    <div class="border rounded-4 p-3 h-100">
                                        <img src="/images/characters/rabbit.png" alt="토끼" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="width: 88px; height: 88px; object-fit: contain;">
                                        <div class="fw-semibold">Lv 16-20</div>
                                        <div class="text-secondary small">토끼</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-4">
                                    <div class="border rounded-4 p-3 h-100">
                                        <img src="/images/characters/dragon.png" alt="드래곤" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="width: 88px; height: 88px; object-fit: contain;">
                                        <div class="fw-semibold">Lv 66-70</div>
                                        <div class="text-secondary small">드래곤</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <p class="text-secondary small mb-2">CORE LOOP</p>
                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2">서비스 핵심 흐름</h2>
                <p class="text-secondary mb-0">회원가입부터 인증, 레벨업, 랭킹 경쟁까지 한 흐름으로 이어집니다.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <span class="badge text-bg-primary mb-3">1</span>
                            <h3 class="h5">오늘의 미션 등록</h3>
                            <p class="text-secondary mb-0">상·중·하 난이도별로 하루 한 개씩 미션을 등록하고 루틴을 시작합니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <span class="badge text-bg-primary mb-3">2</span>
                            <h3 class="h5">사진 인증</h3>
                            <p class="text-secondary mb-0">미션을 완료하면 사진으로 인증하고 즉시 DONE 처리와 보상을 받습니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <span class="badge text-bg-primary mb-3">3</span>
                            <h3 class="h5">EXP와 레벨업</h3>
                            <p class="text-secondary mb-0">난이도에 따라 경험치를 얻고, 누적 EXP가 캐릭터 성장으로 이어집니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <span class="badge text-bg-primary mb-3">4</span>
                            <h3 class="h5">랭킹 경쟁</h3>
                            <p class="text-secondary mb-0">전체 유저와 레벨과 EXP를 비교하며 꾸준함을 기록으로 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-5 bg-white border-top border-bottom">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-4 align-items-start">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                    <p class="text-secondary small mb-2">CHARACTER GROWTH</p>
                    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3">레벨별 캐릭터 성장 예시</h2>
                    <p class="text-secondary">낮은 레벨부터 초월자까지, 루틴이 쌓일수록 시각적으로도 성장 단계를 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>

                    <div class="row g-3 mt-1">
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                            <div class="border rounded-4 p-3 text-center h-100">
                                <img src="/images/characters/chick.png" alt="병아리" class="img-fluid mb-2" style="width: 72px; height: 72px; object-fit: contain;">
                                <div class="fw-semibold small">Lv 6-10</div>
                                <div class="text-secondary small">병아리</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                            <div class="border rounded-4 p-3 text-center h-100">
                                <img src="/images/characters/fox.png" alt="여우" class="img-fluid mb-2" style="width: 72px; height: 72px; object-fit: contain;">
                                <div class="fw-semibold small">Lv 26-30</div>
                                <div class="text-secondary small">여우</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                            <div class="border rounded-4 p-3 text-center h-100">
                                <img src="/images/characters/lion.png" alt="사자" class="img-fluid mb-2" style="width: 72px; height: 72px; object-fit: contain;">
                                <div class="fw-semibold small">Lv 41-45</div>
                                <div class="text-secondary small">사자</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                            <div class="border rounded-4 p-3 text-center h-100">
                                <img src="/images/characters/unicorn.png" alt="유니콘" class="img-fluid mb-2" style="width: 72px; height: 72px; object-fit: contain;">
                                <div class="fw-semibold small">Lv 61-65</div>
                                <div class="text-secondary small">유니콘</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                            <div class="border rounded-4 p-3 text-center h-100">
                                <img src="/images/characters/supernova.png" alt="초신성" class="img-fluid mb-2" style="width: 72px; height: 72px; object-fit: contain;">
                                <div class="fw-semibold small">Lv 91-95</div>
                                <div class="text-secondary small">초신성</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                            <div class="border rounded-4 p-3 text-center h-100">
                                <img src="/images/characters/godsaengler.png" alt="갓생러" class="img-fluid mb-2" style="width: 72px; height: 72px; object-fit: contain;">
                                <div class="fw-semibold small">Lv 100+</div>
                                <div class="text-secondary small">갓생러</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-4 p-lg-5">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-secondary small mb-1">RANKING PREVIEW</p>
                                    <h2 class="h4 mb-0">실시간 랭킹 미리보기</h2>
                                </div>
                                <a href="/ranking" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm">전체 보기</a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="list-group list-group-flush">
                                {{#topRankings}}
                                    <a href="/user/{{nickname}}" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action px-0 py-3">
                                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                                                <img src="{{characterImage}}" alt="{{characterName}}" class="rounded" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; object-fit: contain;">
                                                <div>
                                                    <div class="fw-semibold">{{rank}}위 · {{nickname}}</div>
                                                    <div class="text-secondary small">{{characterName}}</div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="text-end">
                                                <div class="small fw-semibold">Lv. {{level}}</div>
                                                <div class="small text-secondary">EXP {{exp}}</div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </a>
                                {{/topRankings}}

                                {{^topRankings}}
                                    <div class="text-secondary small">아직 랭킹 데이터가 없습니다.</div>
                                {{/topRankings}}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm bg-dark text-white">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-lg-5 text-center">
                    <p class="text-uppercase small opacity-75 mb-2">Start Today</p>
                    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3">오늘의 작은 행동을 성장 기록으로 남기세요.</h2>
                    <p class="opacity-75 mb-4">미션 등록, 인증, 경험치, 캐릭터 성장, 랭킹 경쟁까지 한 흐름으로 시작할 수 있습니다.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center gap-2">
                        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">회원가입</a>
                        <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">로그인</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
</body>
</html>
